---
title: Cal Smart Flakey Barramundi and Grape Pan Sauce with Rosemary Potatoes
description: Elevate fish night with flakey pan-seared barramundi in a sweet-savoury DIY grape pan sauce. Roasted potatoes and fresh greens make a delicious, wholesome base!

